{"title":"斥“骗”功——一个老农的话","authors":["杨玉辰"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"斥“骗”功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一个老农的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨玉辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李洪志，甭装蒜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的功法就叫“骗”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说能“救人免苦难”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法轮”一转危变安；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可你岳父患癌求你治，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你发功却送他上西天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说“有病不用吃药片”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“打坐念佛”身自健；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可你为何感冒也往医院跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"药开少了你还道长短？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法轮功”，尽行骗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗得人跟你上贼船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗得人心散脑错乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗得人家败命也完！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李洪志，甭狡辩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“骗”功戳穿原形现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歪理邪说齐清算！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戳穿“真”“善”“忍”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“真”？不真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸无点墨却著文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求人捉刀本为假，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒名顶替何为真！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“善”？不善。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病危不准上医院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见死不救是为恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落井下石真凶残！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“忍”？不忍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持见不同即怀恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围攻谩骂泄私愤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明祸国又殃民！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“真善忍”，真坑人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是非美丑不能分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝君莫信“真善忍”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重读马列做新人！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}